==========
mac/README
==========

There are important parts of BLT which might also run under MacOS, but
unfortunately I don't have access to a Mac computer, so I depend on the
feedback of Mac folks: if you own such a computer and have managed to get
BLT at least partially running under MacOS, please contribute to the BLT
development by sending your patches to mike@hightec.saarlink.de.


Thanks in advance,
mike
